Choline has been found in increased concentration in breast cancer patients.

 Hypothesis: The choline signal as observed by MRS is sensitive to treatment, and a positive response to treatment will give a reduction in choline concentration.

 The purpose of this study is to establish methods for quantification of choline in breast cancer by MRS